(1054, 'γενεσις', 1161, '1078', 'γένεσις', 'genesis', 5, 'birth, nativity, Mt. 1:18; Lk. 1:14; Jas. 1:23; successive generation, descent, lineage, Mt. 1:1; meton. life, Mt. 1:18; Jas. 3:6*'),
