(2834, 'κραζω', 3189, '2896', 'κράζω', 'krazō', 55, 'to utter a cry, Mt. 14:26; to exclaim, cry out, Mt. 9:27; Jn. 1:15; to cry for vengeance, Jas. 5:4; to cry in supplication, Rom. 8:15; Gal. 4:6 '),
